  panelId: enemy-preview
  title: Enemy Preview
  body: '<sprite="Sword" index=0> is the enemy''s attack, <sprite="hp" index=0> its toughness. Defeating it needs Attack at least equal to <sprite="hp" index=0>; a weak <sprite="shield" index=0> Defend takes <sprite="wound" index=0> Wounds. <sprite="siege" index=0> Siege wins without a counterattack. Some enemies accept <sprite="gem" index=0> Influence and leave peacefully.'
